From 6a62eb38ad713880cbab009084526ff99742487d Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Amy Martin <amy.martin@sfgov.org>
Date: Mon, 2 Feb 2026 15:04:46 -0800
Subject: [PATCH] Improve UI consistency and document handling

- Group documents and PDF links under single Documents section in MediaAssetsCard
- Add support for additional document types (.doc, .docx, .xls, .xlsx, .ppt, .pptx)
- Extract filenames from URLs and display in tooltips for all media assets
- Update card headings to use sentence case (Images and documents, User feedback, Broken links, Other files)
- Update button and link text to use sentence case (Check links, Create new)
- Show documents from metadata first, followed by document links from page content
- Filter out duplicate documents that appear in both metadata and page links
---
